\section{Implementation}
  The Tamil to Malayalam Dictionary App is implemented using a Flutter frontend and a Django REST framework backend, providing users with a smooth and efficient experience for searching Tamil words and retrieving their Malayalam meanings, translations, definitions, and pronunciations. The system is designed with essential features such as search functionality, offline mode, and user authentication, ensuring a user-friendly and efficient experience.\vspace{12pt}\newline The Flutter frontend is responsible for delivering a responsive and intuitive user interface. Users can enter a Tamil word in the search bar, and the app retrieves its meaning and details from the backend API. To enhance usability, the app supports offline mode, allowing users to access previously fetched words and meanings without an internet connection. Additionally, the pronunciation feature helps users listen to the correct pronunciation of words, improving their understanding.\vspace{12pt}\newline The backend, built with the Django REST framework, manages user authentication, word data, and API requests. The system follows a secure authentication process where users sign up using only their email and password. Admins, however, log in using a username. Passwords are securely hashed to enhance security. The backend also enables administrators to add new Tamil words along with their Malayalam meanings, definitions, and pronunciation details through a custom Flutter-based admin panel. The database efficiently stores words and their meanings, ensuring quick and accurate retrieval when a user searches for a word.\vspace{12pt}\newline The integration and deployment of the app ensure smooth communication between the frontend and backend using RESTful API endpoints. The system is optimized for fast response times and seamless navigation. The entire application is deployed on a server, making it accessible to users at any time. The Flutter admin panel allows administrators to manage word entries efficiently, ensuring that the dictionary remains updated and accurate. Overall, the Tamil to Malayalam Dictionary App offers a robust and practical solution for language translation, benefiting users by providing quick and accurate word translations along with pronunciation support. 



